Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:50.30,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,00)\pos(260,322)}区域划分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:50.30,Status,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,00)\pos(274,366)}大地图/有怪物出没
